their sore area, it would be cured. This kofun should not be confused with the {{nihongo|Sekijinsan Kofun|石神山古墳||}} in the city of [[:en:Miyako, Fukuoka|Miyako, Fukuoka]], which has the same name, but written in different ''[[:en:Kanji|Kanji]]''.<ref name="Shiseki"/>
